source: TEXT_SUBWIL013_00571_SEQ_00<tab>Wolkan of the Gladiators' Guild is muttering frantically to himself about an infestation of ladybugs in the region.
target: TEXT_SUBWIL013_00571_SEQ_00<tab>剣術士ギルドのウォルカンは、増えすぎて困っているレディバグの討伐を頼みたいようだ。

source: TEXT_SUBWIL013_00571_SEQ_01<tab>Travel to western Thanalan and slay four of the pestilent ladybugs.
target: TEXT_SUBWIL013_00571_SEQ_01<tab>西ザナラーンに生息している「レディバグ」を4匹討伐しよう。

source: TEXT_SUBWIL013_00571_SEQ_02<tab>You have bravely slain four unsuspecting ladybugs. Return to the Gladiators' Guild and tell Wolkan of your heroic deed.
target: TEXT_SUBWIL013_00571_SEQ_02<tab>レディバグの討伐を完了した。剣術士ギルドにいる「ウォルカン」に報告しよう。

source: TEXT_SUBWIL013_00571_SEQ_03<tab>By felling several nefarious ladybugs, you have made the road through Thanalan a deal safer for traveling merchants.
target: TEXT_SUBWIL013_00571_SEQ_03<tab>無事、冒険者として討伐を達成することができた。きっと商人たちも、魔物に怯えることのない、快適な旅ができるだろう。

source: TEXT_SUBWIL013_00571_TODO_01<tab>Report to Wolkan at the Gladiators' Guild.
target: TEXT_SUBWIL013_00571_TODO_01<tab>剣術士ギルドのウォルカンに報告

source: TEXT_SUBWIL013_00571_WOLKAN_000<tab>Carried yer arse in here lookin' for work, eh? Well, yer in luck. Just so happens I've a deed what needs doin'.
target:
TEXT_SUBWIL013_00571_WOLKAN_000<tab>よぉ、冒険者、仕事を頼まれてくれねェか？
何、初心者でもできる簡単な仕事ってやつさ。

source: TEXT_SUBWIL013_00571_WOLKAN_001<tab>Wild ladybugs've been wreakin' bloody havoc on the outskirts of town. Somethin' in the air of late's made 'em ornery as an aurochs in rut.
target:
TEXT_SUBWIL013_00571_WOLKAN_001<tab>最近天候のせいか、レディバグっていう魔物が
西ザナラーン付近に大量に発生してるらしいんだ。

source: TEXT_SUBWIL013_00571_WOLKAN_002<tab>Ain't much for fightin' on their own, but in numbers they're more than a match for any merchant who's seen more days at the teat than he has on the battlefield.
target:
TEXT_SUBWIL013_00571_WOLKAN_002<tab>単体だとそんなに怖いヤツじゃないんだが、
集団で湧かれると、非力な商人なんかじゃぁちと辛い。

source: TEXT_SUBWIL013_00571_WOLKAN_003<tab>Well, what'll it be? Fancy puttin' down four or so of the bloody buggers, or don't ye?
target:
TEXT_SUBWIL013_00571_WOLKAN_003<tab>すまんが、ちょっと狩ってきてくんねェか？
そうだなぁ、4匹ほど狩れば十分だろ。

source: TEXT_SUBWIL013_00571_WOLKAN_010<tab>Back in one piece, are ye? It's about bloody time.
target: TEXT_SUBWIL013_00571_WOLKAN_010<tab>レディバグを倒してきてくれたか、ありがとよ！

source: TEXT_SUBWIL013_00571_WOLKAN_011<tab>I admit, ye look as though ye just picked up a sword yesterday. But ye handle yerself well enough, I'll give ye that.
target:
TEXT_SUBWIL013_00571_WOLKAN_011<tab>見た感じ、まだまだ新米風のようだが。
なかなかどうして、けっこうやるじゃねェか。

source: TEXT_SUBWIL013_00571_WOLKAN_012<tab>And here, I'll give ye this, as well. Ain't worth a night in Ul'dah's finest pillowhouse, but I'm sure ye'll find a use for it.
target:
TEXT_SUBWIL013_00571_WOLKAN_012<tab>ガキの駄賃程度だが、こいつはほんの礼だ。
それでも、今のお前にとっては悪くない額だろ？
